#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the rotation degree (<guimenuitem>No Rotation (0 Degrees)</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Left (90 Degrees)</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Upside Down (180 Degrees)</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Right "
"(270 Degrees)</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite ugao rotiranja (<guimenuitem>Bez rotacije (0 Stepeni)</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Lijevo (90 stepeni)</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Izvrnuto nadolje (180 Stepeni)</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Desno (270 stepeni)</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Osvježi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the refresh rate (<guimenuitem>Very Low</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Low</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Medium</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>High</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Very High</guimenuitem>). The "
"higher the rate, the more computing power (CPU) will be needed."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite učestalost osvježavanja (<guimenuitem>Vrlo mala</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Mala</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Srednja</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Visoka</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Vrlo visoka</guimenuitem>). "
"Što je veća učestalost to će biti potrebno više procesorske snage."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Colors</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Boje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select different color vision deficiencies to simulate color blindness. This "
"is not useful for people with color blindness, but good for designing "
"accessible interfaces."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite različite vidljive boje da simulirate daltonizam. Ovo nije korisno "
"za daltoniste, ali dobro za dizajniranje pristupačnih interfejsa."

